Package org.e2immu.support

Class FirstThen<S,​T>

java.lang.Object
org.e2immu.support.FirstThen<S,​T>
Type Parameters:
S - type of the initial stage
T - type of the final stage
public class FirstThen<S,​T>
extends java.lang.Object
An object which first holds an object of type S, and, in the second and final stage of its life-cycle, holds an object of type T.

This class is eventually immutable: once the second stage has been reached, its fields cannot be changed anymore. There is no support data and no possibility of content modification; therefore, the type is eventually E2Immutable.
